body:
Sword Unsheathe Recasting is a small RPG sword mod with more complete combat and items, and unique attribute features.
Nearly 50 swords, quite a bit and synthetic materials have been added to the mod, and compared to the original Blade Out of the Sheath, the changes have improved some crafting tables, appropriately strengthened/weakened weapon abilities, and also supplemented the unfinished items of the previous game.

All (normal) swords have their own crafting/acquisition methods, and are positioned for durability and special attributes according to their synthetic values;

Code Storm: Right click to fix durability automatically (coming soon);

LOGO sword: the surface is a sword, but it is actually an all-round tool, and the level is the same as that of the diamond tool;

Loong Rage: Non-flammable, but explosive, when in a riding state, attacking creatures will cause a level 4 explosion;

Abyss Gaze: Ability is combined by awakening and evil spirit apocalypse - right-click air to gain night vision (300 moments), if stealth to get an additional jump boost V (300 moments), hand-held to obtain fire resistance always in effect, attack to make creatures float;

S.C.T.: right button in normal state to get 10 seconds speed I, right button to get 10 seconds speed III when running;

Shadow of Death: Attacking others will wither, and when there is no power effect on the body, you will also wither;

Gold EXtreme: Personal favorite weapon, extremely fast attack speed, high damage (limited technology, models cannot be placed directly in jar bags, if you want to have model effects, you need to install an ideal resource pack);

NotEase Chop: People don't know what it does for the time being.

Can be smelted in a furnace, resetting NBT with durability;

High enchantment value, better enchantment attributes, some weapons cannot be enchanted;

Right-click air or blocks to give players various status effects;

Force speed double A (very few), some weapons sacrifice attack speed plus damage, some sacrifice damage plus attack speed;

Summon lightning strikes and become a 220V Thunder King;

Right-clicking an arrow in the direction of the front sight will consume durability and arrows;

High-tier weapons come with a right-click air or block to restore their durability (limited technology, not possible at the moment).
